author: Wintergatan

One of those GREAT moments: Hearing my song played by a 600 year old clocktower all over Utrecht, Netherlands 🙂

If you want to see a more from this incredible experience and learn more about this amazing clock tower, watch the full video here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6CQgzqYuo04
